name: Taxidermy Moonkin Head
description:
Featured on WoW-Insider! http://wow.joystiq.com/2011/05/19/world-of-warcrafts-moonkin-taxidermy-by-cid-snook/

This is a taxidermy style Moonkin head on a solid wood plaque. It has light up yellow LED eyes! Video of it here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Ag5_8vt9wY&feature=player_embedded

This would make a great and unique addition to your home or business.

34" tall from bottom of plaque to top of antlers and 18" wide.

It is quite heavy so shipping will have to be estimated separately from the purchase price.

name: Ecstasy of Flight Print
description:
Inspired by the Artist Alphonse Mucha this piece depicts a white dragon breaking free of its bonds and rising up above the clouds into the blue moonlit skies.

Each print is signed by the artist and is printed on cardstock.

Measures 9 1/2" x 13 1/2"
